Package spaceInvaders.Model

Class Star

java.lang.Object
spaceInvaders.Model.Star
public class Star extends Object
Represents a star in the Space Invaders game. This class handles the properties and collision detection for a star object.
Version:
1.0
Author:
MD Amanullah

    • isHit

      public boolean isHit(int bulletX, int bulletY, int bulletWidth, int bulletHeight)
      Checks if the star is hit by a bullet. This method is used for collision detection between the star and a bullet.
      Parameters:
      bulletX - The X coordinate of the bullet.
      bulletY - The Y coordinate of the bullet.
      bulletWidth - The width of the bullet.
      bulletHeight - The height of the bullet.
      Returns:
      true if the bullet intersects with the star, false otherwise.
